{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A thrilling <strong>vampire-themed visual novel</strong>,\u00a0Bloodcrave is a tale of love, corruption, and deceit.\u00a0<strong>Player choices</strong>\u00a0have a drastic impact on the outcome of the game, featuring multiple endings and epilogues for each character. Will you lead your companions down the path of virtue, or will you make them succumb to the lure of darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312370/extras/animated_banner_01.gif?t=1734844713\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alex is a young engineer who is saved by Chloe, a fierce vampire hunter, and discovers that his blood holds a secret that could change the balance of power in a <strong>war between vampires and vigilantes</strong>. Will he use his newfound strength to help Chloe rid the city of the ruthless blood suckers, or will he succumb to his dark desires and become a force of destruction?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2312370/extras/animated_banner_02.gif?t=1734844713\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you <strong>plan your actions</strong> for each day, you'll discover hidden quests, events, and animated scenes that bring this captivating world to life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ROMANCE:</strong> <strong>six  love interests</strong>, each with their own unique branching storyline</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>INTRIGUE:</strong> an expansive main story with  <strong>multiple possible different endings</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LOGISTICS:</strong> plan your days carefully, where will you go? who will you spend time with?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>THEATRICS:</strong> fully <strong>voice acted</strong> scenes which bring the world and ch